# OpenSSL binaries
<transform file path=usr/openssl/1.1/bin/.* -> default mode 0555>
<transform file path=usr/openssl/1.1/bin/.* -> default group bin>
<transform file path=usr/openssl/1.1/bin/.* -> default owner root>
